BLUMPS
author: Travis Thompson
contact: travisat@gmail.com

To Compile:

Download:
git clone http://github.com/travisat/blumps.git

In blumps directory run:
make

To Play:

In blumps directory run:
./blumps

Currently there is no way to install.
Once I have gotten it to a more mature state I will start to work on installing it.

Libraries I used to Compile:

libsdl1.2 1.2.14
libglu1-mesa 7.6.1
libftgl2 2.1.3
libsdl-image1.2 1.2.10
libconfig8 1.3.2

if on debian/ubuntu
aptitude install libsdl1.2-dev libglu1-mesa-dev libftgl-dev libsdl-image1.2-dev libconfig8-dev

Also you may need to do this to get ftgl to link with freetype correctly:
As root: ln -s /usr/include/freetype2/freetype/ /usr/include/freetype
